	   <tr><td colspan=2>Though the bloodforge hammer is useable by most melee classes, the bloodforge armor series is useable only by melee dwarves.&nbsp;&nbsp;I can't think of much else that is restricted to just dwarves.  There are a number of paladin only weapons you can strive for.  I believe the first is the falchion of Koada'Vie.  It is listed as a level 22 item and is no drop, so must be earned.  I'm sure that can be done with the help of friends.  Ghoulbane, brilliant sword of faith/soulfire, fiery defender/avenger (someday).<br><br>Souldragoon Flamingheart<br>40th circle Paladin of Virtue<br>Fennin Ro<br>&nbsp;<br><i>Follow virtue, and the virtuous will follow you.</i></td></tr>
