	   <tr><td colspan=2>a two handed practice sword giving you 19dmg 47 dly is a very nice weapon. it is a tad bit slow but keep it for those monsters like ghouls for which you need a magical weapon. but to let you know its worth is about 300 plat depending on server. the proc is a level 22. while looking for a nice magical 1hs weapon for your character not not take haste. your whip has a small attack to a great dly and that will bring up your skill lvl's quickly. if you have a couple plat set aside (around 60) go to the oasis and you can buy a combine. you dont have to save up your money and buy some thing better later on. 7dmg 28 dly from your whip is fine for your lvl. later on when you get several hundred plat saved get yourself a runed falcion or a crytaline blade. then by 28 if you are in a good guild they will help you get ghoulbane.<br><br>one way to make money is to do the GLS quest. but never fear. not many people know this and i will tell you paladins this. there is a gypsie in the oasis that you can turn the GLS in to. she will give you the book then turn it in to here for 8 to 9 plat. go to all the gypsies and see which gives you the best offer. this is i little known fact that you can sit in oasis and auction for GLS's and people will sell them to you. but keep it quite. :)<br>&nbsp;<br>Celtpirate Waverider<br>34 paladin<br>saryrn-Boche Morte<br>Yoshiro<br>15 cleric<br>saryrn-House of Wargoth</td></tr>
