	   <tr><td colspan=2>I have to agree with Souldraggon on the best sites for auctions.&nbsp;&nbsp;However, he left out Greater Feydark near the orc lifts. At least on my server, players are constantly auctioning of various articles in that zone.  Of course, it helps to auction yourself on the items which you want to procure (i.e. I picked up my Axe of the Iron Back this way).  Or, if your lucky someone will walk up to you and ask you if you would like to purchase and item (this happened to me when I aquired my Crystaline Blade for a mere 50pp- a steal).  Just keep your eyes open and read those pesky green chat messages.<br>&nbsp;<br>Dadin <br>54th Cavalier<br>Honored Circle on Xev<br><br>Dwarven Thane<br>Hellwinds - Palomides </td></tr>
